What you need to know:  The competition, which begins on March 5 in various wards across the county is a brainchild of Governor Jonathan BiiA total of 275 teams have registered with 215 being men's while 60 teams will compete in the women's categoryAccording to Governor Bii, the idea to hold the Governor's Cup was hatched last year when he noticed volleyball nets in various shopping centres during his campaigns for the gubernatorial seat